  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/f1e738e6619d8d4d34cf3688929cd59f.poster.avif?t=1742916808\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/f1e738e6619d8d4d34cf3688929cd59f.webm?t=1742916808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/f1e738e6619d8d4d34cf3688929cd59f.mp4?t=1742916808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Celebrity Kombat</strong> is a casual fan game of fighting games made by indies. We are improving the game day by day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Celebrity Kombat</strong>, every character is famous and unique, and has its strengths and weaknesses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/894398b7e10f210ab51caf6e492ebf25.avif?t=1742916808\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras_big/894398b7e10f210ab51caf6e492ebf25.avif?t=1742916808 width=800 height=368 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be ready to fight with the all-time most famous, richest, and extravagant people of this world. From Nicki Minaj to Cardi B, passing by Kanye West to Jay-Z, discover their style and secret techniques to win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New characters added weekly!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/b2df6e920e43dfe3854095306c723b86.avif?t=1742916808\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras_big/b2df6e920e43dfe3854095306c723b86.avif?t=1742916808 width=800 height=364 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every character has its own style: sword, magic, close combat, karate... The choice is yours and there's a lots more to discover!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/6ef7f5537401abab6b43adbf4afaa4de.avif?t=1742916808\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras_big/6ef7f5537401abab6b43adbf4afaa4de.avif?t=1742916808 width=800 height=366 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play offline or online: play with a friend on your computer with two controllers, or play with a completely random stranger online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be Ready For the Ultimate Fight with celebrities!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/f1e738e6619d8d4d34cf3688929cd59f.poster.avif?t=1742916808\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/f1e738e6619d8d4d34cf3688929cd59f.webm?t=1742916808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/f1e738e6619d8d4d34cf3688929cd59f.mp4?t=1742916808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Celebrity Kombat</strong> is a casual fan game of fighting games made by indies. We are improving the game day by day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Celebrity Kombat</strong>, every character is famous and unique, and has its strengths and weaknesses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/894398b7e10f210ab51caf6e492ebf25.avif?t=1742916808\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras_big/894398b7e10f210ab51caf6e492ebf25.avif?t=1742916808 width=800 height=368 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be ready to fight with the all-time most famous, richest, and extravagant people of this world. From Nicki Minaj to Cardi B, passing by Kanye West to Jay-Z, discover their style and secret techniques to win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New characters added weekly!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/b2df6e920e43dfe3854095306c723b86.avif?t=1742916808\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras_big/b2df6e920e43dfe3854095306c723b86.avif?t=1742916808 width=800 height=364 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every character has its own style: sword, magic, close combat, karate... The choice is yours and there's a lots more to discover!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras/6ef7f5537401abab6b43adbf4afaa4de.avif?t=1742916808\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240390/extras_big/6ef7f5537401abab6b43adbf4afaa4de.avif?t=1742916808 width=800 height=366 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play offline or online: play with a friend on your computer with two controllers, or play with a completely random stranger online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be Ready For the Ultimate Fight with celebrities!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
